relation: One Spook Too Many - The Complete Series
The heroes are hyper and have a little too much time on their hands.
My take on the chaotic, dramatic battle between the Universal Cosmic Destroyer, Giygas, and the Chosen Four.
Orange Kid has gone insane and has teamed up with Pokey, building "Orange Kidsteins." Ness, Jeff, Poo, Picky, and Apple Kid team up to save Paula and the world.
The legend continues even if it is 1000 years into the future.
Three months after the journey to save the Earth is over, Ness returns to his normal life. However, he still misses Paula, and even more so under the light of the moon.

My labor of love. I started the day the funfest started, and only ended today, the last day of the funfest. In word 2007, it had over 35 pages.....its a lot of reading, but I hope if anyone is brave enough to read it all, that they will like it.
A story from the eyes of Lucky, one of the Runaway Five. After he gives an interviewer a dissatisfying answer to a question, he rethinks it and musters up his best answer to make up for it.
Originally submitted for the 2010 EarthBound Fanfest, this short story follows a formerly nondescript NPC through a night of romance, adventure, and terror with some of Summers' strangest characters.
Ness and Paula's first date doesn't go entirely as planned.
